d encounters, he reveals that our fascination with Nordic societies and our love for Nordic music might be more intertwined than first thought.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Classical.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073923708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311074977940uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300265491?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300265491423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300265491/original  a978-3-11-073923-7  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074977-9  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY